General Science Toolkit
│
├── 1. User Interface Layer
│   ├── Web App GUI (React, HTML/CSS)
│   ├── Command Line Interface (CLI)
│   └── API Access Endpoints (REST, GraphQL)
│
├── 2. Application Logic Layer
│   ├── Workflow Orchestrator
│   │   ├── Task Scheduler
│   │   └── Dependency Manager
│   ├── Input/Output Handler
│   │   ├── File Parsers (CSV, JSON, XML)
│   │   └── Data Validators
│   └── Session/State Manager
│
├── 3. Computational Core
│   ├── Domain-Specific Modules
│   │   ├── Physics Engine
│   │   ├── Chemistry Simulator
│   │   ├── Biological Modeler
│   │   └── Environmental Data Analyzer
│   ├── Math & Statistics Tools
│   │   ├── Numerical Solvers (ODE, PDE)
│   │   ├── Statistical Models (Regression, ANOVA)
│   │   └── Optimization Algorithms
│   └── Machine Learning Toolkit
│       ├── Preprocessing Pipelines
│       ├── Model Training & Evaluation
│       └── Model Deployment
│
├── 4. Data Layer
│   ├── Data Sources
│   │   ├── Local Datasets
│   │   ├── Remote APIs (NASA, NCBI, NOAA)
│   │   └── Repositories (Zenodo, Dryad)
│   ├── Data Management
│   │   ├── Database Interfaces (SQL, NoSQL)
│   │   └── Metadata Handlers
│   └── Caching & Storage Layer
│
└── 5. Utility & Integration Layer
    ├── Visualization Engine (Matplotlib, D3.js, Plotly)
    ├── Logging & Debugging Tools
    ├── Export Utilities (PDF, LaTeX, Excel)
    └── External Plugin Support (e.g., Jupyter, R Markdown)
